This software, SANDJA (the "Software"), was conceived, designed, and developed
by KWANG Techs Hub (collectively, the "Rights Holders") within the
context of a competitive hackathon. The entirety of its source code,
architecture, concepts, user interface designs, algorithms, data models,
business logic, and all other constituent elements constitute original works of
authorship protected by applicable copyright law, trade secret law, and
intellectual property regulations.

This repository is made publicly accessible solely for the purpose of
hackathon evaluation and demonstration. Public availability does NOT constitute
a grant of any rights beyond those explicitly enumerated in this license.

